    {
        "content": "<p>This code raise an error \"permission denied\"</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">createFile</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">path</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">FilePath</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">content</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">String</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">IO</span> <span class=\"n\">Unit</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"k\">do</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">let</span> <span class=\"n\">h</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚Üê</span> <span class=\"n\">IO.FS.Handle.mk</span> <span class=\"n\">path</span> <span class=\"n\">IO.FS.Mode.write</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">h.putStr</span> <span class=\"n\">content</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 410541700,
        "sender_full_name": "Asei Inoue",
        "timestamp": 1703938699
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I managed to reach this code:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">createFile</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">path</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">FilePath</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">content</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">String</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">IO</span> <span class=\"n\">Unit</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"k\">do</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">match</span> <span class=\"n\">path.parent</span> <span class=\"k\">with</span>\n  <span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"n\">none</span> <span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">IO.FS.writeFile</span> <span class=\"n\">path</span> <span class=\"n\">content</span>\n  <span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"n\">some</span> <span class=\"n\">parent</span> <span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">IO.FS.createDirAll</span> <span class=\"n\">parent</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">IO.FS.writeFile</span> <span class=\"n\">path</span> <span class=\"n\">content</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 410542775,
        "sender_full_name": "Asei Inoue",
        "timestamp": 1703939844
    },
